role in SEO (Search Engine Optimization).
&nbsp;

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:10.720
You might notice that when you&nbsp;
search for any topic on YouTube,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:17.680
shorts appear first. Because its SEO is perfect.&nbsp;
And those types of videos get long time views. 
